  "prompt": "What are the jersey numbers of famous soccer players?",
  "response": "Certainly! Here are some famous soccer players and their jersey numbers:\n\n1. **Lionel Messi** - Primarily known for wearing number 10 at FC Barcelona and number 30 at Paris Saint-Germain.\n2. **Cristiano Ronaldo** - Famously wears number 7, often referred to as \"CR7.\"\n3. **Neymar Jr.** - Typically wears number 10 for both Paris Saint-Germain and the Brazil national team.\n4. **Kylian Mbapp\u00e9** - Wears number 7 at Paris Saint-Germain.\n5. **Pel\u00e9** - Historically known for wearing number 10.\n6. **Diego Maradona** - Renowned for wearing number 10.\n7. **Zinedine Zidane** - Wore number 10 during his time at Juventus and number 5 at Real Madrid.\n8. **David Beckham** - Known for wearing number 7 at Manchester United and number 23 at Real Madrid and LA Galaxy.\n9. **Ronaldinho** - Famously wore number 10 during his time at FC Barcelona.\n10. **Thierry Henry** - Often associated with number 14 during his time at Arsenal.\n11. **Andrea Pirlo** - Known for wearing number 21 at Juventus and in the Italian national team.\n12. **Luis Su\u00e1rez** - Often wears number 9.\n\nThese numbers can be iconic and associated with their respective players, contributing to their legacy in soccer history.",
